title: October Debuts: Not Reading is the Great Pumpkin, Charlie Brown!
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.

The month being October 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, obviously.

This instalment contains the following current debuts:


   Butterfly     #1 (of 4) - Archaia      - Crime / Drama / Mystery

   Father's Day  #1 (of 4) - Dark Horse   - Crime / Drama / Mystery

   Fiction Squad #1 (of 6) - Boom Studios - Crime / Fantasy / Traditional


Only three titles this time. Note the total lack of Image! And yes, "Butterfly" and "Father's Day" are even more similar than the identical genre listings suggest, as it happens! :P

As bonuses, there are two half-issue-length previews, for a change. Based on their contents, I'm definitely intrigued, but have not yet altogether made up my mind about the previewed titles one way or the other. Plus, I included the #2 issue for one of the series, simply because both fell into the release window corresponding to last month
